    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个数据处理流程图。最上面是数据库DB，然后向下指向一个包含三个模块的处理块，中间那个模块要突出显示，因为它比较宽，处理的数据量大。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "db",
        "block:ID",
        "A",
        "B",
        "C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，DB用圆形表示，下面用箭头down指向一个block块，里面放A、B、C三个子模块。您说B要突出，是指视觉上要加宽，还是要特殊样式？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "db",
        "blockArrowId6",
        "B",
        "style"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "B既要显示为宽文本，也要加粗边框和填充色，让它一眼就能看出来是核心模块。然后处理块下面要有个D模块，C和整个处理块都要能连到D。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "D",
        "ID -- D",
        "C -- D",
        "stroke",
        "width"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把结构搭出来：DB在顶部，箭头向下到block块，里面A、B、C纵向排列，B显示为'A wide one in the middle'，下面留空后放D。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "db",
        "blockArrowId6",
        "block:ID",
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "space",
        "D"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "等等，布局上我们只用一列，这样纵向流程更清晰。还有B的样式，填充用浅紫色，边框深灰色，stroke-width要4px。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "columns 1",
        "style B",
        "fill",
        "stroke",
        "stroke-width"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "收到，设置columns 1单列布局，B的样式加上fill:#f9F, stroke:#333, stroke-width:4px。现在处理块ID和C都连到D，这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "columns 1",
        "style B",
        "ID -- D",
        "C -- D"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "C到D的连接没问题，但ID到D的连接表述要确认一下——是整个处理块指向D，不是里面的A或B单独连。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ID -- D",
        "block:ID"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，ID -- D表示整个block块指向D，C -- D是子模块C的独立连接。这样结构就完整了：DB→处理块→D，加上C的旁路连接，B高亮显示。",
